snippet.title: Amber Heard tells the court that Johnny Depp 'threw bottles like grenades'
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has claimed Johnny Depp hurled "30 or so glass bottles" at her "like grenades", during a "three-day hostage situation" she alleges took place in Australia in March 2015.

The actress gave evidence for a third day at the High Court in London in Mr Depp's libel hearing against The Sun newspaper. 

Witnesses included her former make-up artist who claims she had to cover up bruises on Ms Heard's face for an appearance on 'The Late Late Show with James Corden' in 2015.
